<p>If you have a website for the local market of Warsaw or Lublin, SEO audit will cost less than if it is a small website or a store for the whole Poland. SEO audit precedes all further activities performed by us within website positioning. These are multi-faceted and multi-stage actions. SEO optimization includes primarily checking such issues as:</p>

